Description:
------------
The code included in this package helps in converting some of the
Indian Language HTML pages from proprietary encodings to 
standard UTF8 encoding.


Requirements:
-------------
PHP-5

Suggestions:
------------
The users should have unicode fonts for each language and Indic enabled 
browser to view the Indian Language Characters properly.

Some of the unicode fonts for different languages,

Kannada   - Kedage
Malayalam - Anjalioldlipi
Tamil     - TSCu_Paranar
Telugu    - Pothana2000
Hindi, Marathi etc.  - Gargi
(for Devanagari scripts)
